subject: FROM SUPREME COURT OF UNITED STATES.
body:
*FROM SUPREME COURT OF UNITED STATES.*
*THREE-ARMS ZONE P.M.B 308. GARIABUJA.*
*Address: **1 First Street, NE Washington, DC 20543
<https://www.google.com/maps/search/1+First+Street,+NE+Washington,+DC+20543?entry=gmail&source=g>*
*From: John G. Roberts, Jr Chief,*
*Justice of the Supreme Court of UNITED STATES*

Attention: Please,

I am John G. Roberts, Jr, Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of UNITED
STATES. I wish to inform you that
we

have received your email regarding the required Diplomatic Immunity Seal of
transfer Certificate which you have been directed by the FBI to contact
this office for instructions on how to obtain the said certificate.

We have concluded every necessary arrangement regarding obtaining the said
certificate on your behalf, right now the only thing delaying the needed
document by the FBI is the required issuing fee of $100 which you are to
send to us immediately to enable us to obtain the required document on your
behalf as soon as possible.

However, I want to guarantee you 100% that the document will be obtained on
your behalf immediately. The fee of $100 is received from you before the
end of the day.

Meanwhile, we have also received instruction from the FBI to release the
certificate to you once the needed fee is received, and we understand that
you have less than 24 hours to obtain the needed certificate, therefore you
have been advised to urgently send the needed fee to us, to enable us
obtain the certificate on your behalf without any further delay.

Due to the urgency of this matter, you are advised to send the fee to my
receiving agent with the below stated Receiver's Data / information send $
100 buy any of the listed Card, Steam Wallet Card Or iTunes Gift Card. $100
and attached the copy,

Furnish this office with the payment details involving your full
information, once the payment is made, in order for us to obtain the
document on your behalf immediately. Please call me at my direct cell phone
number as soon as you send the fee today. You can email me your direct cell
phone number so that I can call you as soon as the document is obtained on
your behalf here in my office.

Yours Faithfully,
John G. Roberts, Jr
CHIEF JUSTICE OF THE SUPREME
UNITED STATES OF AMERICA.
